      "questionText": "<p>$$ \\begin{aligned} &\\mathrm{CH}_3-\\mathrm{CH}=\\mathrm{CH}_2+\\mathrm{NOCl} \\rightarrow \\mathrm{P}\\\\ &\\text { Identify the adduct. } \\end{aligned} $$</p>",
      "options": [
